dcterms:description: A standard dataset used for experiments in AMR-to-text generation, containing 16,833 instances for training, 1368 for development, and 1371 for test. Each instance includes a sentence and an AMR graph.
dcterms:title: AMR corpus (LDC2015E86)

dcterms:description: An external dataset used to supplement the AMR corpus with large-scale automatic data by sampling raw sentences for training.
dcterms:title: Gigaword
